ge=54,65|url=http://www.psa-peugeot-citroen.com/fr/pagebuilder/downloadpackage/2293?pid=-1|publisher=PSA Peugeot Citro\u00ebn|accessdate=2014-09-26|language=fr}}{{dead link|date=August 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" |55,900<ref name=\"PSA Annual Report 2014\"/>\n|{{TBA}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Citro\u00ebn Elys\u00e9e}} \n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20060616205459/http://citroens.citroen1.info/China/dongfeng.htm CITRO\u00cbNS: Donfeng]\n*[http://www.citroenet.org.uk/foreign/china/fukang/elysee.html Citro\u00ebn Elys\u00e9e at Citro\u00ebn\u00ebt]\n\n{{Citro\u00ebn}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Citroen Elysee}}\n[[Category:Citro\u00ebn vehicles|Elysee]]\n[[Category:Dongfeng vehicles]]\n[[Category:Front-wheel-drive vehicles]]\n[[Category:Cars of China]]\n[[Category:2010s cars]]\n[[Category:Compact cars]]\n[[Category:Sedans]]\n[[Category:Touring cars]]\n[[Category:Cars introduced in 2002]]\n", "text_old": "{{more citations needed|date=September 2014}}\n{{Infobox automobile\n| name         = Citro\u00ebn Elys\u00e9e\n| aka          = Citro\u00ebn C-Elys\u00e9e\n| image        = Citro\u00ebn C-Elys\u00e9e II facelift China 2017-03-24.jpg\n| caption      = Second generation Citro\u00ebn C-Elys\u00e9e\n| manufacturer = [[Citro\u00ebn]]\n| production   = 2002\u2013present\n}}\n\nThe '''Citro\u00ebn Elys\u00e9e''' is a [[Small family car|small family]] [[Sedan (car)|saloon car]] produced for the [[China|Chinese]] domestic market by the [[Dongfeng Peugeot-Citro\u00ebn Automobile]], a [[joint venture]] between the [[France|French]] [[PSA Group]] ([[Peugeot]]-[[Citro\u00ebn]]) and the Chinese manufacturer [[Dongfeng Motor]]. Production commenced in June 2002.\n\n==First generation (2002\u20132013)==\n{{Infobox automobile\n| name         = Citro\u00ebn Elys\u00e9e\n| aka          = Citro\u00ebn C-Elys\u00e9e\n| image        = Citro\u00ebn Elys\u00e9e China 2012-06-16.JPG\n| interiorimage= 